snippet.title: Indie Dev Story Steam Trailer
snippet.description:
Quit your job to become an indie developer and make your first game!
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/746520/Indie_Dev_Story/
A single-player 'clicker' game that tries to mimic the frantic feeling of being an indie developer; make your game while trying to stay healthy, social and earning enough money to pay the bills.
#indiedev #gamedev
